OL,3,CIdris Elba waxwork unveiled at Madame
OL,4,CTussauds
OL,6,FActor Idris Elba has said it is
OL,7,F"surreal" to have his likeness made
OL,8,Finto a waxwork at Madame Tussauds in
OL,9,FLondon.
OL,11,FThe 53-year-old's waxwork, his first
OL,12,Ffigure at the Baker Street attraction,
OL,13,Fis kitted out in a long-sleeve version
OL,14,Fof the suit that he wore to meet the
OL,15,FKing in July 2024.
OL,17,FThe figure is also wearing a pair of
OL,18,Fpatent Christian Louboutin dress
OL,19,Fshoes, which have been donated to the
OL,20,Fmuseum by Elba.
