OL,6,FThe Hackney-born actor said it was
OL,7,F"amazing" to see himself in the London
OL,8,Fattraction.
OL,10,FHe said: "It's truly an honour to be
OL,11,Frecognised in this way and even more
OL,12,Fspecial to know this other version of
OL,13,Fme will be standing tall in London.
OL,15,F"So, even when I'm away, a part of me
OL,16,Fis always at home."
