OL,4,CTussauds
OL,6,FElba, best known for his roles as
OL,7,FStringer Bell in The Wire and as TV
OL,8,Fdetective Luther, has been involved
OL,9,Fwith the attraction's artists for
OL,10,Fmonths, and called the process
OL,11,F"fascinating".
OL,13,FHe said: "It's not dissimilar to
OL,14,Fprepping for a movie role ` working
OL,15,Fwith talented artists to flesh out the
OL,16,Fcharacter, getting the costume just
OL,17,Fright, but this time it's for me.
