OL,3,CIdris Elba waxwork unveiled at Madame
OL,4,CTussauds
OL,6,F"It's really surreal to see another
OL,7,Fversion of me standing in Madame
OL,8,FTussauds London, it feels like a full
OL,9,Fcircle moment."
OL,11,FElba has more recently been seen on
OL,12,Fscreens in apocalyptic thriller A
OL,13,FHouse Of Dynamite, and Disney's family
OL,14,Ffilm Zootopia 2.
OL,16,FThe actor was appointed an Officer of
OL,17,Fthe Order of the British Empire (OBE)
OL,18,Fin 2016 for his services to drama by
OL,19,FQueen Elizabeth II.
