OL,6,FHe is also the face behind the Don't
OL,7,FStop Your Future campaign, launched in
OL,8,F2024, which aims to raise awareness of
OL,9,Fserious youth violence and knife crime
OL,10,Fin the UK.
OL,12,FElba has since met with the King twice
OL,13,Fto discuss this matter and creating
OL,14,Fpositive opportunities for young
OL,15,Fpeople.
OL,17,FSteve Blackburn, general manager at
OL,18,FMadame Tussauds London, said: "It's a
OL,19,Fprivilege to be able to create Idris's
OL,20,Ffirst-ever figure right here in
OL,21,FLondon, where it all began.
